reviewText: I found a Region 0 copy of this in an Orlando record store. This is the complete Buenos Aires show from 1992. The source is PRO #1a. If you know what that means, then you will know what to expect and you will be very happy to have a professionally-pressed DVD of this source. If you have no idea what I am talking about, then you will probably end up complaining about the quality.

while i never expected Caligula, the description led me to believe some (simulated) sex would be taking place; i kept waiting, and waiting, but it never came (ALL puns intended). that might not have been the death blow, except the movie makes NO SENSE AT ALL, without any naked people, and dry humpin'.
